to describe that user.

87
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:57,290
With features like these
you can then come up

88
00:03:57,290 --> 00:04:01,060
with a feature vector
x subscript u,

89
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:04,560
use as a user superscript
j for user j.

90
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,980
Similarly, you can also
come up with a set of

91
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:09,890
features for each
movie of each item,

92
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:12,650
such as what was the
year of the movie?

93
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:16,280
What's the genre or genres
of the movie of known?

94
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:19,475
If there are critic
reviews of the movie,

95
00:04:19,475 --> 00:04:22,760
you can construct one
or multiple features to

96
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,380
