126
00:05:43,370 --> 00:05:46,000
That's okay too. In
content-based filtering,

127
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,520
we're going to develop an
algorithm that learns to

128
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:51,250
match users and movies.

129
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:53,650
Previously, we were predicting

